What would be the best way to develop technologies in order to avoid collisions, if not the imitation of existing barriers sensors in nature?
For example, that one of the abeyors.
In a surprising project presented at the CEATEC in Japan, the abjorros gave the starting point for Nissan engineers to design the next generation of collision prevention systems.
